* Make sure php5 or newer is installed and pdo_mysql or pdo_sqlite extensions
  enabled
* Copy files to directory accessible by your webserver
* Copy config.ini.template to config.ini and modify to suit your configuration,
  especially database details and station elevation and location must be set
  correctly
* Modify files in about/${lang}.phtml in a way you like, these are shown when
  user opens 'About station' page
